es)%20and%20divide%20it%20by%20the%20amount%20of%20cash%20you%20plan%20on%20investing%20in%20the%20property%20that%20year%20(this%20could%20be%20your%20down%20payment%20or%20the%20purchase%20price%20of%20the%20home%20if%20you%20bought%20it%20in%20cash).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20my%20opinion%2C%20you%20cannot%20write%20an%20offer%20until%20you%20have%20learned%20what%20average%20is%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Zuber.%20%26quot%3BBecause%20once%20you%20know%20the%20average%20%E2%80%94%20say%20it's%205%25%20%E2%80%94%20then%20you%20can%20feel%20confident%20about%20writing%20offers%20that%20produce%207%25%20or%208%25%20or%209%25%20cash-on-cash.%20The%20magic%20of%20this%20business%20is%20simply%20getting%20above-average%20yield.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-build-a-portfolio-rental-properties-real-estate-investing-2025-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1760002202000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68caa6b0183847aa39d6eb9a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-build-a-portfolio-rental-properties-real-estate-investing-2025-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BThe%20more%20you%20know%20your%20buy%20box%2C%20the%20better%20your%20chances%20are%20at%20finding%20a%20great%20deal%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20real%20estate%20investor%20told%20Business%20Insider.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kelkins%40businessinsider.com%20(Kathleen%20Elkins)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-build-a-portfolio-rental-properties-real-estate-investing-2025-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Banijay%20Kids%20%26amp%3B%20Family%20Unveils%20Its%20First%20Digital-First%20Original%20Series%2C%20%E2%80%98Ava%20%26amp%3B%20Digger%2C%E2%80%99%20Teaming%20With%20TheSoul%20Publishing%20(EXCLUSIVE)%26nbsp