%20to%20support%20you%2C%20their%20local%20regulations%20like%20at%20the%20city%20and%20county%20level%20of%20towns%20that%20can%20interfere%20with%20a%20project%20and%20set%20a%20project%20back%2C%20billions%20of%20dollars%2C%26quot%3B%20Andrew%20Feldman%20said%20during%20a%20recent%20appearance%20on%20Harry%20Stebbings'%2020VC%20podcast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20Business%20Insider%2C%20Feldman%20expanded%20on%20his%20view%20that%20local%20regulations%20are%20holding%20back%20major%20AI-related%20infrastructure%20projects%20like%20energy%20production.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20they%20have%20been%20able%20to%2C%20at%20a%20national%20level%2C%20stand%20up%20vast%20amounts%20of%20power%2C%20and%20they've%20done%20it%20by%20building%20massive%20dams%2C%20by%20burning%20coal%2C%20by%20doubling%20down%20on%20solar%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20CEO%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20they%20have%20put%20together%20an%20extraordinary%20power%20infrastructure%2C%20and%20I%20think%20the%20plan%20benefited%20from%20some%20form%20of%20central%20decision-making.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFeldman%20said%20the%20US%20shouldn't%20try%20to%20simply%20steal%20China's%20playbook%2C%20but%20rather%20find%20better%20ways%20to%20support%20AI%20investments%20through%20the%20existing%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20a%20fragmented%20political%20system%2C%20but%20there%20is%20no%20reason%20why%20we%20should%20have%20local%20ordinances%20interfering%20with%20the%20development%20of%20power%20projects%2C%20with%20the%20development%20of%20data%20centers%2C%20the%20very%20sort%20of%20things%20that%20power%20big%20AI%20deployments%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20no%20reason%20we%20should%20have%20a%20patchwork%20of%20AI%20regulations%2C%20meaning%20that%20each%20company%2C%20like%20Cerebras%20or%20OpenAI%2C%20has%20to%20think%20differently%20in%20each%20state%3B%20that's%20just%20a%20tax%20on%20innovation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFeldman%20said%20a%20moratorium%20on%20state-level%20AI%20laws%2C%20similar%20to%20the%20one%20Sen.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsenators-strike-ai-provision-from-big-beautiful-bill-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETed%20Cruz%20pushed%20unsuccessfully%3C%2Fa%3E%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20would%20be%20a%20good%20step.%20Cruz's%20initial%20policy%2C%20which%20was%20ultimately%20stripped%20out%20of%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20%26quot%3BOne%20Bill%20Beautiful%20Bill%2C%26quot%3B%20would%20have%20blocked%20state%20and%20local%20AI%20laws%20for%20a%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20maybe%20a%205-year%20moratorium%20would%20be%20a%20nice%20starting%20point%20with%20an%20option%20to%20renew%20on%20five%2C%26quot%3B%20Feldman%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20industry%20is%20moving%20fast%3B%20this%20market%20is%20moving%20unbelievably%20quickly.%20I%20think%20we%20should%20do%20things%20that%20advantage%20our%20AI%20companies%2C%20both%20large%20and%20small.%20I%20don't%20think%20it's%20enough%20to%20advantage%20just%20the%20largest.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20chipmaker%2C%20Cerebras%20is%20in%20the%20thick%20of%20the%20AI%20race.%20Unlike%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENvidia%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20dominates%20the%20GPU%20market%2C%20Cerebras%20makes%20massive%20chips%20specifically%20designed%20for%20AI%2C%20roughly%20the%20size%20of%20a%20dinner%20plate.%20The%20company%20had%20planned%20to%20go%20public%2C%20but%20last%20week%20formally%20filed%20to%20withdraw%20its%20IPO.%20Feldman%20has%20said%20that%20Cerebras%20still%20intends%20to%20go%20public%20but%20wants%20to%20update%20its%20filing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGiven%20that%20the%20business%20has%20improved%20in%20meaningful%20ways%20we%20decided%20to%20withdraw%20so%20that%20we%20can%20re-file%20with%20updated%20financials%2C%20strategy%20information%20including%20our%20approach%20to%20the%20rapidly%20changing%20AI%20landscape%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20on%20LinkedIn%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFeldman%20doesn't%20see%20the%20US%20gaining%20ground%20in%20the%20AI%20race%20by%20making%20China%20more%20reliant%20on%20an%20American%20tech%20stack%2C%20a%20view%20that%20conflicts%20with%20the%20likes%20of%20Nvidia%20CEO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjensen-huang%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EJensen%20Huang%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Huang%20is%20trying%20to%20get%20the%20Trump%20administration%20to%20sign%20off%20on%20approval%20for%20Nvidia%20to%20sell%20more%20advanced%20chips%20to%20Chinese%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20Feldman%20would%20like%20to%20see%20the%20US%20do%20more%20to%20incentivize%20European%20allies%2C%20along%20with%20Qatar%2C%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%2C%20and%20Saudi%20Arabia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20there%20is%20a%20much%20richer%20debate%20to%20be%20had%20whether%20we%20should%20be%20selling%20them%20down%20rev%20technologies%20and%20that%20may%20or%20may%20not%20be%20the%20right%20thing%20to%20do%2C%20but%20we%20should%20absolutely%20not%20sell%20our%20absolute%20best%20to%20a%20political%20adversary%2C%26quot%3B%20Feldman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcerebras-ceo-andrew-feldman-china-us-ai-race-energy-2025-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1760000941000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68e6bea5cc993f9955cfd29b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcerebras-ceo-andrew-feldman-china-us-ai-race-energy-2025-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Cerebras%20CEO%20Andrew%20Feldman%20says%20China's%20centralized%20policy%20has%20fueled%20its%20advantage%20in%20standing%20up%20%26quot%3Bvast%20amounts%20of%20power.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22bgriffiths%40insider.com%20(Brent%20D.%20Griffiths)%22%2C%22en