%20the%20bull%20run%20reminded%20him%20of%20the%20hype%20and%20speculation%20during%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-internet-dotcom-bubble-tech-stocks-nvidia-market-crash-gordon-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edot-com%20bubble%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20late%201990s%20and%20the%20housing%20bubble%20in%20the%20mid-2000s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20made%20no%20sense%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThings%20just%20kept%20going%20up%20and%20up%20and%20up.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDietrich%20said%20of%20the%20internet%20bubble%2C%20%26quot%3BI'd%20go%20to%20a%20party%20and%20everybody%20was%20telling%20me%20what%20dot-com%20stock%20that%20they%20had%20just%20gotten%20into.%20The%20same%20thing%20is%20happening%20today.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia%20shares%20have%20soared%20about%2013-fold%20since%20the%20start%20of%202023%2C%20catapulting%20the%20chipmaker%20to%20a%20%244.5%20trillion%20market%20capitalization.%20That%20figure%20exceeds%20the%20combined%20value%20of%20Berkshire%20Hathaway%2C%20JPMorgan%2C%20Walmart%2C%20Eli%20Lilly%2C%20and%20Visa.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDietrich%2C%20who%20manages%20money%20for%20private%20investors%2C%20institutions%2C%20and%20retirement%20funds%2C%20said%20he%20believed%20AI%20would%20%26quot%3Bchange%20everything%26quot%3B%20but%20added%20that%20valuations%20were%20%26quot%3Bout%20of%20whack.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20just%20think%20there%20is%20no%20limit%20on%20these%20things%2C%20but%20there%20always%20is%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20Dietrich%20added%20that%20blue-chip%20stocks%20such%20as%20Microsoft%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fbig-short-michael-burry-growth-stocks-market-crash-fed-inflation-2022-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etanked%20during%20the%20dot-com%20crash%3C%2Fa%3E.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20enterprise-software%20giant's%20shares%20fell%2063%25%20over%20the%20course%20of%202000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20he%20was%20alarmed%20about%20retail%20investors%20using%20borrowed%20money%20to%20place%20bigger%20and%20riskier%20bets%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20amplify%20their%20returns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMore%20people%20are%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fburt-malkiel-market-timing-advice-passive-investing-meme-stocks-etf-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eleveraged%20ETFs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20especially%20in%20technology%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe've%20never%2C%20ever%20seen%20a%20big%20market%20downturn%20with%20the%20kind%20of%20leverage%20that%20I%20see%20underlying%20the%20stock%20buying.%20This%20is%20my%20biggest%20worry%20right%20now.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20market%20starts%20going%20down%2C%20you%20want%20to%20get%20out%20of%20those%20things%20really%20quickly%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDietrich%20said%20the%20government's%20injection%20of%20trillions%20into%20the%20economy%20over%20the%20past%20five%20years%20may%20have%20shored%20up%20demand%20and%20staved%20off%20trouble.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20pushed%20off%20the%20recession%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20it%20hasn't%20repealed%20the%20laws%20of%20gravity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22df5ad72f-e14e-4362-9a5d-e2af4003c0ac%5C%22%3EWhere%20to%20invest%20if%20AI%20is%20a%20bubble%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDietrich%20predicted%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-the-secretive-world-of-americas-ai-data-centers-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esprawling%20data%20centers%3C%2Fa%3E%20supporting%20AI%20would%20become%20a%20%26quot%3Bcommodity%20business%2C%26quot%3B%20with%20their%20makers%20becoming%20the%20%26quot%3Butilities%20of%20the%20future%26quot%3B%20and%20looking%20more%20like%20AT%26amp%3BT%20than%20Apple.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20centers%20require%20huge%20amounts%20of%20energy%20and%20water%20to%20run.%20That%20makes%20utilities%20%26quot%3Bprobably%20one%20of%20the%20best%20investments%20for%20a%20long%20period%20of%20time%20going%20forward%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20especially%20as%20they%20can%20switch%20energy%20sources%20as%20needed%20and%20regulators%20ensure%20they%20earn%20sufficient%20profits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20invest%20in%20a%20utility%20because%20they're%20going%20to%20get%20this%20guaranteed%20return%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20calling%20it%20a%20%26quot%3Bquasi-bond%26quot%3B%20as%20it%20pays%20large%20and%20reliable%20dividends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDietrich%20also%20said%20it%20%26quot%3Bmakes%20sense%26quot%3B%20to%20invest%20in%20gold%2C%20which%20breached%20%244%2C000%20a%20troy%20ounce%20for%20the%20first%20time%20this%20week.%20He%20added%20that%20all%20his%20clients%20have%20at%20least%2025%25%20of%20their%20portfolios%20in%20the%20metal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20financial%20guru%20said%20he%20was%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgold-price-today-best-year-1979-bullion-record-high-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebullish%20on%20gold%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%20he%20believed%20the%20US%20government%20was%20trying%20to%20devalue%20the%20dollar%20to%20make%20exports%20more%20competitive%20and%20reduce%20the%20real%20value%20of%20the%20national%20debt%2C%20making%20it%20easier%20to%20pay%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGold%20can%20also%20be%20a%20good%20hedge%20against%20inflation%20accelerating%20because%20of%20tariffs%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwedbush-dietrich-ai-boom-stock-market-bubble-recession-gold-utilities-2025-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1760000401000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68e663b55dbc4fd10daa6a81%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwedbush-dietrich-ai-boom-stock-market-bubble-recession-gold-utilit