%20rivals.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20tech%20giant%20is%20%26quot%3Bganging%20up%26quot%3B%20on%20OpenAI%2C%20said%20a%20Thrive%20Capital%20partner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20an%20episode%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BUncapped%26quot%3B%20podcast%20released%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20Vince%20Hankes%20said%20Big%20Tech%20companies%20don't%20want%20new%20players%20entering%20their%20league.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20mental%20model%20for%20you%20on%20how%20the%20competitive%20landscape%20looks%20like%20is%3A%20OpenAI%20is%20in%20a%20corner%20and%20every%20Big%20Tech%20company%20has%20a%20bazooka%20pointed%20at%20them%20to%20try%20to%20take%20them%20down%2C%26quot%3B%20Hankes%20said.%20%26quot%3BBecause%20none%20of%20those%20Big%20Tech%20companies%20want%20a%20new%20Big%20Tech%20company.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fseed-100-best-early-stage-vc-investors-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EThrive%20Capital%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20founded%20by%20Josh%20Kushner%20in%202011%2C%20is%20a%20major%20investor%20in%20the%20ChatGPT%20maker.%20The%20venture%20capital%20firm%20has%20also%20invested%20in%20companies%20including%20SpaceX%2C%20Databricks%2C%20and%20Stripe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20should%20want%20it%20to%20be%20a%20competitive%20fair%20fight%20for%20a%20new%20company%20to%20break%20into%20Mag%20Seven%2C%26quot%3B%20Hankes%20added%2C%20referring%20to%20Apple%2C%20Microsoft%2C%20Amazon%2C%20Alphabet%2C%20Meta%2C%20Tesla%2C%20and%20Nvidia.%20%26quot%3BBecause%20that's%20what%20our%20whole%20ecosystem%20lives%20and%20breathes%20off%20of.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20support%20for%20OpenAI%20doesn't%20mean%20the%20VC%20firm%20only%20plans%20to%20invest%20in%20the%20AI%20giant%2C%20Hankes%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20isn't%20a%20risk-adjusted%20better%20return%20than%20OpenAI%2C%20and%20therefore%20if%20we're%20given%20a%20decision%2C%20we%20should%20do%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20about%20investing%20more%20in%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20you%20can't%20not%20take%20a%20risk%20because%20of%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHankes%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%20month%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ea%20string%20of%20deals%20and%20announcements%20has%20positioned%20%24500%20billion%20OpenAI%20closer%20to%20some%20of%20its%20more%20established%20tech%20competitors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20its%20DevDay%20event%20on%20Monday%2C%20the%20company%20announced%20it's%20bringing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-just-launched-app-store-taking-aim-apple-google-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eapps%20inside%20ChatGPT%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20CEO%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fsam-altman%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ESam%20Altman%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20now%20has%20800%20million%20weekly%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20also%20unveiled%20an%20app%20software%20development%20kit%20that%20allows%20developers%20to%20build%20their%20own%20apps%20for%20ChatGPT.%20This%20makes%20the%20AI%20tool%20more%20like%20an%20app%20store%2C%20a%20move%20that%20could%20threaten%20industry%20leaders%20like%20Apple%20and%20Google.%20Google%20investors%20have%20already%20been%20concerned%20about%20ChatGPT%20and%20other%20generative%20AI%20tools%20eating%20into%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt-search-market-share-google-openai-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGoogle's%20search%20engine%20share%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20OpenAI%20announced%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-amd-chips-deal-nvidia-ai-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Emulti-year%20deal%20with%20AMD%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%2