-steps-tips%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Born%20in%20a%20Mumbai%20Slum%2C%20This%20Inspiring%20Dropout%20Uses%20Football%20To%20Keep%2026000%20Kids%20in%20School%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20Ashok%20Rathod%20was%2018%2C%20he%20began%20gathering%20children%20from%20Mumbai%E2%80%99s%20Ambedkar%20Nagar%20slum%20for%20weekend%20football%20matches.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20he%20had%20no%20great%20plan%20%E2%80%94%20just%20a%20desire%20to%20keep%20kids%20away%20from%20addiction%2C%20child%20marriage%2C%20and%20dropping%20out%20of%20school%2C%20which%20had%20consumed%20many%20of%20his%20own%20friends.%20What%20started%20as%20a%20small%20effort%20grew%20into%20the%20OSCAR%20(Organization%20for%20Social%20Change%2C%20Awareness%20and%20Responsibility)%20Foundation%20in%202010%20%E2%80%94%20an%20organisation%20that%20today%20has%20touched%20thousands%20of%20young%20lives%20across%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20those%20lives%20is%20that%20of%20Yamini.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20rainy%20afternoon%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20a%20shy%20Class%209%20student%20walked%20nervously%20into%20a%20ground%20where%20the%20OSCAR%20Foundation%20had%20gathered%20children.%20She%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20anyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20data-tracker%3D%5C%22%7B%26quot%3Barticle_name%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3BArticle%20Page%20Ad%20Banner%26quot%3B%2C%26quot%3Bposition%26quot%3B%3A1%2C%26quot%3Barticle_id%26quot%3B%3A496964%7D%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcampaign.thebetterindia.com%2Ftbi-showcase%2F%5C%22%20data-carousel%3D%5C%22adbanner%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Article%20Ad%20Banner%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fad-banner-1756106894.jpg%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3